<div><head>張諮涼記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.2">天錫字公純嘏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.3">安定烏氐人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.4">張耳後也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.5">曾祖軌。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.6">永嘉中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.7">為涼州刺史，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.8">值京師大亂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.9">遂據涼土。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.10">天錫篡位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.11">自立為涼州牧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.12">苻堅使將萇攻沒涼州，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.13">天錫歸長安。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.14">堅以為侍中北部尚書歸義侯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.15">從堅至壽陽。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.16">堅軍敗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.17">遂南歸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.18">拜散騎常侍西平公。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.19">《世說》注二。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.20">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.21">此引作《張資涼州記》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-1a.22">下同。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-2a.2">天錫明鑒穎發，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-2a.3">英聲少著。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1304_CHANT_001-2a.4">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
